high_descs: Turn around and face the center of the table to the right of the silver range.
Pick up the loaf of bread to the right of the microwave on the table.
Turn to the left, move past the range, then turn to left and then move and face the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator door, place the loaf of bread on the top shelf above the blue plate, let it cool in the refrigerator, then open the refrigerator door, pick up the loaf of bread, and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn to the left, move past the blue coffee maker, then turn right and face the table to the left of the dishwasher.
Place the loaf of bread on the table between the head of lettuce and the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread on the table.

high_descs: Turn around to face the white kitchen table.
Pick the bread up from off of the table.
Turn around and go to the right to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the bread inside, close the refrigerator, wait a few seconds, open the refrigerator, pick up the bread, and close the refrigerator.
Move to the left to face the white kitchen table.
Place the bread on the white kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: Place the refrigerated bread on top of the white table.

high_descs: Turn around to face the white table with the toaster on top.
Pick up the loaf of bread from the table.
Carry the bread to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the bread on the top shelf, close the door, and then remove after a couple seconds.
Turn and carry the bread to the white table on your right, which is just past the dishwasher.
Place the loaf of bread in the back right corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a loaf of cold bread on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and position yourself in front of the white table with the toaster on it.
Pick up the loaf of bread to the right of the toaster.
Turn left and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the fridge so you are facing it.
Chill the bread on the top shelf and then retrieve it making sure to close the door when you are done.
Turn left and walk until you see a white table on your right and then turn right to face it.
Place the chilled bread above the blue plate on the right side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled loaf of bread on top of a table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward and turn right again to face the white table with the toaster on it.
Pick up the loaf of bread next to the toaster.
Turn left and walk toward the wall, then turn left again and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the bread on the bottom shelf, close the door, wait a moment and open the fridge door again and take the bread back out.
Turn left and walk toward the cupboard, then turn right to the white table with the lettuce on it.
Place the bread on the white table behind the blue plate.
anns.task_desc: Move bread from one table to another, refrigerating it in between.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter.
Pick the loaf of bread up.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Place the loaf of bread on the top shelf of the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it back out.
Turn left and take a couple steps and then face the white table on the right.
Place the loaf of bread in front of the spatula on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread on a table.
